title: 6 Chess Books - July 2016 (gnv64)
description:
This torrent contains 6 chess books in PDF formats. Two each on openings, endings & game collections:

1. David Bronstein - Fifty Great Short Games by Nukolay Minev
2. Fighting the French - A New Concept by Denis Tevseev
3. Rudolf Spielmann - Fifty Great Short Games by Nukolay Minev
4. Tactical Chess Endings by John Nunn
5. The Budapest Gambit - Up-to-Date Coverage of a Dangerous Gambit by Bogdan Lalic
6. The Chess Endgame Study - A Comprehensive Introduction (2nd Ed) by A,J,Roycroft
